===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|-}}

# {{uncountable}} Condensed [[water]] falling from a [[cloud]].
# {{uncountable}} {{figurative}} Any matter moving or falling, usually through air, and especially if liquid or otherwise figuratively identifiable with [[raindrop]]s.
